WPPConnect API REST (1.0)

Download OpenAPI specification:Download

Authentication

httpBearer

Security Scheme Type HTTP
HTTP Authorization Scheme bearer

Auth

generate-token (Gera token Bearer para sessão)

Authorizations:
httpBearer
    path Parameters
    secretkey
    required
    string
    Example: THISISMYSECURETOKEN

    (Required) chave do admin

    Responses

    http://localhost:21465/api/{session}/{secretkey}/generate-token

    Response samples

    • 201
    Content type
    application/json
    {
    • "status": "Success",
    • "session": "nova",
    • "token": "$2b$10$N9xrdqCW4S1jpNyB44L1nuXj79EAvo83MS6uxhBg8JOvWNLV8QlaS",
    • "full": "nova:$2b$10$N9xrdqCW4S1jpNyB44L1nuXj79EAvo83MS6uxhBg8JOvWNLV8QlaS"
    }

    start-session (Retorna QRCode de login)

    Inicializa a sessão

    Authorizations:
    httpBearer
      Request Body schema: application/json
      webhook
      required
      string

      Responses

      http://localhost:21465/api/{session}/start-session

      Request samples

      • Payload
      Content type
      application/json
      {
      • "webhook": "https://webhook.site/7cc2944d-3967-4cea-988c-d57ea80bce5f"
      }

      status-session (Atualiza QRCode de login)

      Retorna o status da session

      Authorizations:
      httpBearer

        Responses

        http://localhost:21465/api/{session}/status-session

        qrcode-session (Pegar qrCode de autenticação via stream)

        Retorna o status da session

        Authorizations:
        httpBearer

          Responses

          http://localhost:21465/api/{session}/qrcode-session

          check-connection-session (status da conexão)

          Verifica se a sessáo esta conectada

          Authorizations:
          httpBearer

            Responses

            http://localhost:21465/api/{session}/check-connection-session

            close-session

            finaliza a sessão

            Authorizations:
            httpBearer

              Responses

              http://localhost:21465/api/{session}/close-session

              Chat

              Chat Methods

              All Chats

              Retrieves all chats

              Authorizations:
              httpBearer
                header Parameters
                Content-Type
                required
                string
                Example: application/json

                Responses

                http://localhost:21465/api/{session}/all-chats

                Chat By Id

                Retrieves chat object of given contact id

                Authorizations:
                httpBearer
                  header Parameters
                  Content-Type
                  required
                  string
                  Example: application/json

                  http://localhost:21465/api/{session}/chat-by-id

                  Chat Is OnLine

                  Checks if a CHAT contact is online.

                  Authorizations:
                  httpBearer
                    header Parameters
                    Content-Type
                    required
                    string
                    Example: application/json

                    Responses

                    http://localhost:21465/api/{session}/chat-is-online

                    Response samples

                    • 200
                    Content type
                    application/json; charset=utf-8
                    {
                    • "status": "success",
                    • "response": false
                    }

                                required
                                string
                                Example: application/json

                                                          Send Reply

                                                          Envia um arquivo para um número de telefone.

                                                          Authorizations:
                                                          httpBearer
                                                            Request Body schema: application/json
                                                            phone
                                                            required
                                                            string
                                                            message
                                                            required
                                                            string
                                                            messageId
                                                            required
                                                            string
                                                            isGroup
                                                            required
                                                            boolean

                                                            Responses

                                                            http://localhost:21465/api/{session}/send-reply
